# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 2024-06-23

**MoodMap: Global Emotions** does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information.

- All mood submissions are fully anonymous and are not linked to any user identity.
- No registration or login is required to use the app.
- Location data is only used to show your mood on the map and is never stored or shared with third parties.
- No data is sold, rented, or disclosed to any other parties.
- If you contact us via email or GitHub Issues, your email address is only used to respond to your inquiry.

If you have any questions, please contact us via [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/zcanzu/moodmap/issues) or our [GitHub Profile](https://github.com/zcanzu).

**This policy may be updated in the future. Please check this page for updates.**
